This Maven project is related to posts on my blog: 

http://makingdevsimple.blogspot.com 

(Specifically, posts that use the Vehicle Service source examples).

Read the MAVEN_SETUP file before running a Maven build.

Includes:

- In-container testing using Arquillian
- JAX-RS with RestEasy and Spring
- Unit testing JAX-RS resources using RestEasy MockDispatcher
- RestEasy JAXB and JSON providers for automated conversion
- Database testing with DBUnit, JPA and HSQL
- Spring Integration tests for wider component testing
- Maven profiles for multi-container builds and multi-container Arquillian tests
